It's a good thing
he decided to hit a ship.

607
00:30:20,651 --> 00:30:22,353
At least that way,
it was contained.

608
00:30:22,386 --> 00:30:24,923
I think he wanted
to introduce the
biological agent

609
00:30:26,223 --> 00:30:27,291
then have all
the passengers
go to their houses

610
00:30:27,324 --> 00:30:28,459
all over the United States

611
