00:31:32,523 --> 00:31:34,125
I've seen a few
like this before.

643
00:31:34,158 --> 00:31:35,626
It's consistent
in text and style

644
00:31:35,659 --> 00:31:37,261
with the one
Al Qaeda released

645
00:31:37,294 --> 00:31:39,530
just before the bombings
in Kenya and Tanzania.

