near Kosovo in 1984
by Serge Kurbsky.

713
00:37:51,935 --> 00:37:55,606
This... is very, very bad.

714
00:37:56,006 --> 00:37:57,607
What is it?

715
00:37:57,641 --> 00:38:01,312
