You got him?

812
00:43:15,291 --> 00:43:16,760
Sweetie, it's all right.

813
00:43:16,793 --> 00:43:18,929
It's okay.
We're right here.

814
00:43:18,962 --> 00:43:21,231
Yeah. You can go
right here.

815
00:43:25,235 --> 00:43:27,170
There. You feel better?

816
00:43:27,203 --> 00:43:29,139
Peter, will you
wait here with him?

817
00:43:29,172 --> 00:43:30,774
I'll be right back.

818
00:43:35,745 --> 00:43:37,080
Is Dr. Krystof around?

819
00:43:37,113 --> 00:43:38,815
MAN:
In X ray.

820
00:43:38,848 --> 00:43:40,217
Excuse me. Dr. Krystof?

821
00:43:40,250 --> 00:43:42,152
Dr. Krystof, please,
I've got a problem.

822
00:43:42,185 --> 00:43:44,254
I have two patients
