823
00:43:44,287 --> 00:43:45,656
I may have three.

824
00:43:45,689 --> 00:43:47,024
Where's that CDC memo?

825
00:43:47,057 --> 00:43:48,892
Station.

826
00:43:48,925 --> 00:43:51,261
(<i> quietly</i> ):
Oh, God.

827
00:43:51,294 --> 00:43:52,863
We're filling up with patients.

828
00:43:52,896 --> 00:43:54,164
Flu symptoms and stomach pains.

829
00:43:54,197 --> 00:43:55,298
What's going on?

830
00:43:55,331 --> 00:43:57,234
Working on it.

831
00:43:57,267 --> 00:43:58,734
Sweet Lord.

832
00:43:58,768 --> 00:44:00,103
Are we in trouble.

833
00:44:00,136 --> 00:44:02,839
48 hours from
infection to symptoms.

834
00:44:02,872 --> 00:44:04,942
Two days ago.

835
00:44:05,942 --> 00:44:08,879
Oh, no. Oh, no.

836
00:44:10,080 --> 00:44:11,982
Oh, God...

837
00:44:20,457 --> 00:44:23,093
I know this sounds strange,
but by any chance

838
00:44:23,126 --> 00:44:25,696
did your mother recently
go to a baseball game?

839
