Yes. She's got
season tickets.

840
00:44:27,931 --> 00:44:29,967
She's a big fan.

841
00:44:46,316 --> 00:44:48,952
Wait for the doctor
to come.

842
00:44:59,395 --> 00:45:01,031
Judy.

843
00:45:12,475 --> 00:45:16,880
Now... a tactical weapon

844
