in four locations:

845
00:45:22,085 --> 00:45:24,855
here... here...

846
00:45:24,888 --> 00:45:27,491
here... and here.

847
00:45:27,524 --> 00:45:29,292
Simple, no?

848
00:45:29,325 --> 00:45:32,495
The virus amplifies itself
through the population

849
00:45:33,129 --> 00:45:34,897
cough by cough

850
00:45:34,931 --> 00:45:36,199
until, of course, finally

851
