the population crash.

852
00:45:38,001 --> 00:45:39,870
Mr. Zenkovsky, I
don't understand.

853
00:45:39,903 --> 00:45:41,805
We got hit in L.A. and Chicago

854
00:45:41,838 --> 00:45:43,106
and indirectly in Houston

855
