No good
for bio-weapon.

870
00:46:15,471 --> 00:46:17,541
Bio-weapons hate the rain.
High winds, daylight.

871
00:46:17,574 --> 00:46:22,079
Sir, the director
needs to see you.

872
00:46:22,579 --> 00:46:24,414
He's in your office.

873
00:46:24,447 --> 00:46:26,383
Excuse me.

874
00:46:26,416 --> 00:46:28,285
SULLIVAN:
So we need
to find out

875
00:46:28,318 --> 00:46:30,487
