So, it's official, Eric.

878
00:46:35,491 --> 00:46:37,894
We bombed
the wrong people.

879
00:46:37,927 --> 00:46:41,231
Well, I'm sure
they deserved it
for something.

880
00:46:41,264 --> 00:46:42,599
Anything on Kurbsky?

881
00:46:42,632 --> 00:46:44,034
We know that he
