persuasive.

1036
00:54:26,028 --> 00:54:27,830
Look, um, you
should know

1037
00:54:27,863 --> 00:54:30,667
that he's showing signs
of the disease.

1038
00:54:30,700 --> 00:54:32,035
I have a suit.

1039
00:54:32,068 --> 00:54:34,337
Even with a monkey suit

1040
00:54:34,370 --> 00:54:36,973
you're a braver man
than me.

1041
00:54:44,046 --> 00:54:45,915
