1042
00:54:49,418 --> 00:54:51,054
We know who you are,
Mr. Hamdoon.

1043
00:54:51,087 --> 00:54:53,956
We know that you were
a professor in Baghdad

1044
00:54:53,989 --> 00:54:55,625
that you speak English

1045
00:54:55,658 --> 00:54:58,028
that your sister and your family
were killed

1046
00:54:58,894 --> 00:54:59,794
in the bombing of your city.

1047
00:54:59,829 --> 00:55:02,832
We know about Dr. Kurbsky
and the bio-weapon

1048
00:55:02,865 --> 00:55:05,435
and your colleague
and the cruise ship.

1049
00:55:05,468 --> 00:55:08,571
You want to see a picture
of your colleague?

1050
00:55:10,606 --> 00:55:12,375
Oh no.
Don't turn your head.

1051
00:55:12,408 --> 00:55:13,910
There's more.

1052
00:55:13,943 --> 00:55:15,712
There is more.

1053
00:55:15,745 --> 00:55:16,846
Hmm.

1054
