Avery, Sharon.
Grandmother, dead.

1056
00:55:26,155 --> 00:55:28,057
Baumgold, Celia.

1057
00:55:28,090 --> 00:55:29,792
Businesswoman, dead.

1058
00:55:29,825 --> 00:55:33,997
Habib, Malik.
