1067
00:55:58,954 --> 00:56:03,360
I need to know
where Dr. Kurbsky is.

1068
00:56:05,761 --> 00:56:08,698
Tell me where
Dr. Kurbsky is.

1069
00:56:12,201 --> 00:56:13,936
Where's Kurbsky?

1070
00:56:13,969 --> 00:56:16,472
Tell me.

1071
00:56:16,505 --> 00:56:17,874
Kurbsky-- where is...

1072
00:56:28,117 --> 00:56:29,853
I'm okay, I'm okay!
Just get him!

1073
00:57:21,270 --> 00:57:23,573
(<i> labored breathing</i> )

1074
00:57:29,278 --> 00:57:31,548
KRYSTOF:
Judy? Judy?

1075
00:57:32,781 --> 00:57:35,918
Oh... oh, my God,
I'm so sorry.

1076
00:57:35,951 --> 00:57:37,053
It's all right.

1077
00:57:37,086 --> 00:57:38,154
There's so much
work to do.

1078
00:57:38,187 --> 00:57:39,622
We could all
use a catnap.

