00:57:39,655 --> 00:57:42,225
JUDY:
Timmy, sweetheart.

1080
00:57:42,258 --> 00:57:44,461
He's dead. I just checked him.

1081
00:57:46,962 --> 00:57:48,564
Did you know him?

1082
00:57:48,597 --> 00:57:51,667
Um, yes.

1083
00:57:51,700 --> 00:57:52,801
That's his father.

1084
00:57:52,835 --> 00:57:54,170
He works with my husband.

1085
00:57:54,203 --> 00:57:57,273
I'd be surprised if he
regained consciousness.

1086
00:57:57,306 --> 00:57:59,141
Probably better
that way.

1087
00:57:59,174 --> 00:58:01,277
Does he have
any more family here?

1088
00:58:01,310 --> 00:58:03,913
No. His wife passed away
two years ago.

1089
00:58:03,946 --> 00:58:05,882
He has a little girl, Abigale.

1090
00:58:05,915 --> 00:58:07,817
She's at his sister's house.

1091
00:58:07,850 --> 00:58:09,218
I'll put in
the order.

1092
00:58:09,251 --> 00:58:11,120
I'll do it.
I want you to go over

1093
00:58:11,153 --> 00:58:12,555
to the Federal Building.

1094
00:58:12,588 --> 00:58:14,223
The Army and the CDC
have converted

1095
00:58:14,256 --> 00:58:16,792
the underground parking into
a massive field hospital.

1096
00:58:16,825 --> 00:58:18,294
Well, what do you
want me to do?

1097
00:58:18,327 --> 00:58:20,630
Beg for supplies.

1098
00:58:27,236 --> 00:58:29,672
MAN (<i> over TV</i> ):
In a bold attempt
to isolate the virus

1099
00:58:29,705 --> 00:58:31,240
and to prevent it from spreading

1100
00:58:31,273 --> 00:58:34,210
the president has ordered the
citizens of the United States

1101
00:58:34,243 --> 00:58:35,678
to remain in their homes.

1102
00:58:35,711 --> 00:58:37,212
Rioting has been reported

1103
00:58:37,246 --> 00:58:40,850
in Chicago, Phoenix,
Los Angeles and San Diego.

1104
00:58:40,883 --> 00:58:42,551
On the international front

1105
00:58:42,585 --> 00:58:44,320
Iraq has continued to move
its army

1106
00:58:44,353 --> 00:58:46,689
towards the Saudi Arabian
border, and the United States

1107
00:58:46,722 --> 00:58:49,058
is sending arms and supplies

1108
00:58:49,892 --> 00:58:50,692
to reinforce that border.

1109
00:58:50,726 --> 00:58:52,328
What do you think the
president'll do

1110
00:58:52,361 --> 00:58:54,096
if Iraq goes
into Saudi Arabia?

1111
00:58:54,129 --> 00:58:55,998
I don't know. It's pretty
hard to send ground troops

1112
00:58:56,031 --> 00:58:58,200
to the Persian Gulf
when they're all busy
in the streets

1113
00:58:58,233 --> 00:58:59,635
trying to enforce
this curfew.

1114
00:58:59,668 --> 00:59:02,805
Probably bomb 'em
back to Babylonia.

1115
00:59:02,838 --> 00:59:04,206
And the Russians?

1116
00:59:04,239 --> 00:59:05,808
The Russians are going
to back down.

1117
00:59:05,841 --> 00:59:07,343
They have to.

1118
00:59:07,376 --> 00:59:09,912
Let's hope they
don't apply the
same logic to us.

1119
00:59:09,945 --> 00:59:11,314
That's World
War III.

