00:59:55,858 --> 00:59:59,829
that we're all going to die?

1133
00:59:59,862 --> 01:00:03,032
No. Only about 25%.

1134
01:00:03,065 --> 01:00:06,268
The good news is, if we don't
sustain another bio-hit

